@startuml
title Calculator — Module-Level Component Dependencies (issue #391)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "__main__\n(entry point)" as Main
component "cli" as CLI
component "interactive" as Interactive
component "operation_registry" as Registry
component "calculator" as Calc

note top of Main
  if CLI args → run_cli(); sys.exit(rc)
  else → run_interactive_session()
end note

Main --> CLI : if len(sys.argv) > 1
Main --> Interactive : else (no args)

CLI --> Registry : instantiates per invocation
CLI --> Calc : instantiates per invocation

Interactive --> Registry : instantiates once per session
Interactive --> Calc : instantiates once per session

Registry --> Calc : composition\n(introspects at construction)

@enduml
